   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click the All Tabs icon (<image placement="inline" href="../attachments/195691351/195691343.png"/>) and select <uicontrol>Config
                  Settings</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select <uicontrol>Display Action Settings</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>From the <uicontrol>Display Type</uicontrol> list, select <uicontrol>Cart Page</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Add a new action <uicontrol>Analyze Deal</uicontrol> and select <uicontrol>Display As</uicontrol> Action.
               </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="317"
                         placement="break"
                         width="600"
                         href="../attachments/195691351/195691344.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <result id="result_lsx_j33_rcc">The action button is available in the cart.</result>
